dct_title_s: Sketch map of the basin of the Mahanuddy (Central India) to accompany the Paper by R. Temple Esqre
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Railways, lines of traffic, direction of proposed tramway, and course of proposed canal are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London, Vol. 35, (1865), pp. 70-74; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.35 1865.
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1865.
